### Welcome to Skylight Pages.
Skylight is the easiest, simplest SDK to create bots in [Everybody Edits](http://everybodyedits.com/). It supports quickly connecting to EE via Kongregate, Facebook, or EverybodyEdits; joining levels; receiving information from levels through a simple event system; and performing actions in a level. It is written in C# and supports any .NET language in the 4.0 or higher framework.

    Room R = new Room("PWjThDaofKbEI");
    Bot B = new Bot(R);
    public static void main()
    {
        B.LogIn();
        B.Join();
    }

    // Wow that was too easy.

